These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, fonseca, davidoff
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, july, january
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, musician, security-guard
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, trance, jazz
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, lizard
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, pink, white
1. the musician is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the security-guard is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's birthday is in july##2
8. the person who likes green is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar      | davidoff     | fonseca      | bolivar      |
| Birthday          | july   | february   | january       |
| Job   | security-guard | lawyer | musician    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | hip-hop    | trance    |
| Pet           | fish    | lizard    | chinchilla |
| Color     | pink  | white     | green        |

