.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, tea
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, october
City: hamburg, paris, london
House: palace, victorian, cape-cod
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, balloon-flower
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, baccarat, siglo
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the victorian house##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is between the cape-cod house and the person drinking tea##2
7. the person traveling to paris is between the person traveling to london and the person who growsballoon-flower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola        | tea      |
| Birthday          | august    | october       | january  |
| City   | london     | paris | hamburg    |
| House   | cape-cod | palace   | victorian    |
| Flower           | tulip      | daffodil  | balloon-flower      |
| Cigar         | siglo    | baccarat      | dunhill |

