.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, fonseca, bluemaster
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, brazilian, egyptian
House: cape-cod, palace, craftsman
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, brown, chestnut
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, woodworking, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, tram
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who likes chestnut##2
3. the brazilian is on the far left##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the game-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the egyptian##1
7. the person who likes brown is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3      |
| Cigar      | bluemaster     | game   | fonseca      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | egyptian  | nigerian  |
| House   | cape-cod       | palace  | craftsman        |
| Color           | chestnut       | brown   | blood-red |
| Hobby         | woodworking      | sudoku | traveling   |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram     | helicopter |

 